    By: BG Haute

    Our price: $440.00

    BG Haute E01015 dress. If youre going for ritzy glamour, you wont be disappointed by this sheath that has gorgeous sequin embroidery. The strapless neckline and fitted bodice create a very sexy mid-section with a curvy shape and bare-skin exposure. Illusion sequins provide a bit of a thrill by with a flesh-toned backing that plays a little bit of peek-a-boo.
